OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FHer parents - Katie and John - hand
OL,7,Fdelivered a letter to Number 10
OL,8,Fcalling for legal changes to help
OL,9,Fprevent similar tragedies in the
OL,10,Ffuture in January 2026.
OL,12,FKatie said: "It's really hard to put
OL,13,Finto words what it means to lose your
OL,14,Fchild. But I think the only thing you
OL,15,Fcan say is it's catastrophic to your
OL,16,Flife and we never want any other
OL,17,Ffamily to live with what we've had to
OL,18,Flive with."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
