FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FNursery deputy manager Kate Roughley,
OL,7,Fwas found guilty of manslaughter and
OL,8,Fjailed for 14 years in May 2024.
OL,10,FCCTV captured nine-month-old Genevieve
OL,11,Fstruggling to breath after being
OL,12,Ftightly swaddled and strapped face
OL,13,Fdown on a beanbag for more than an
OL,14,Fhour and a half at Tiny Toes nursery
OL,15,Fin, Stockport, in May 2022.
OL,17,FA nearly identical case happened in
OL,18,Fthe West Midlands, when 14-month-old
OL,19,FNoah Sibanda was placed face down on a
OL,20,Fcushion with a blanket over his head.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FThe government have now released a
OL,7,Fletter outlining plans to tighten
OL,8,Fsafety rules in the Early Years
OL,9,FFoundation Stage.
OL,11,FIt says: "Genevieve Meehan's death in
OL,12,F2022 was a devastating tragedy that
OL,13,Fshould never have happened. Our
OL,14,Fthoughts remain with Genevieve's
OL,15,Fparents, family members and others
OL,16,Fthat have been affected by this.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,F"Children's safety is at the very
OL,7,Fheart of this government's plan for
OL,8,Fchange and, as Minister for Early
OL,9,FYears, the safety of our children is
OL,10,Fmy utmost priority."
OL,12,FThe government plan is for all early
OL,13,Fyears settings to follow new safe
OL,14,Fsleep requirement from September.
OL,16,FThe guidelines will provide clarity
OL,17,Ffor early years providers around safe
OL,18,Fsleeping practices - and include
OL,19,Frequirements for children under two to
OL,20,Fbe placed to sleep on their backs,
OL,21,Fwith their heads uncovered.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FIt also confirms that cots should not
OL,7,Fcontain any extra items such as toys,
OL,8,Fpillows and blankets, and children's
OL,9,Fheads should not be covered.
OL,11,FGenevieve's dad, John, said:
OL,12,F"Previously we just had parental
OL,13,Fguidance and that had to be adapted by
OL,14,Fnurseries for nursery settings. Now we
OL,15,Fhave specific requirements for safe
OL,16,Fsleep which leaves Ofsted and
OL,17,Fnurseries in absolutely no doubt about
OL,18,Fwhat needs to be done to keep children
OL,19,Fsafe."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FCheshire Day Nursery in Thelwall - who
OL,7,Falready have their own safe sleep
OL,8,Fpolicy - are welcoming the guidance.
OL,10,FManager Charlotte Harrison said: "We
OL,11,Ffully support the changes and that are
OL,12,Ffully implemented within our setting.
OL,13,FIt's something that really does need
OL,14,Fto be brought to light for all parents
OL,15,Fwhether the children go to a nursery
OL,16,For other settings it's very important
OL,17,Fthat all practitioners are following
OL,18,Fthe guidance that's been put out."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1774897908
OL,3,CParents of Genevieve Meehan welcome
OL,4,Cnew safe sleeping rules in nurseries
OL,6,FCampaigners are also welcoming the
OL,7,Fguidance, with Ofsted and baby safety
OL,8,Fcharity the Lullaby Trust involved in
OL,9,Fwriting the guidance.
OL,11,FLullaby Trust CEO Jenny Ward said: "It
OL,12,Fis a standardisation that we haven't
OL,13,Fseen in this amount of detail before.
OL,15,F"Before, settings have been told they
OL,16,Fshould follow safe sleep advice but
OL,17,Fwhat we've done here is really detail
OL,18,Fthat out so there is no question about
OL,19,Fhow that should be and how babies
OL,20,Fshould be slept."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
